## ✅ Deployment Checklist

### Pre-Deployment
- [ ] Run `flutter pub get`
- [ ] Run `flutter test`
- [ ] Run `flutter analyze`
- [ ] Check `flutter format`

### Build
- [ ] `flutter build web --release`
- [ ] Verify build size < 5MB
- [ ] Check PWA manifest
- [ ] Verify service worker

### Deploy
- [ ] `git add .`
- [ ] `git commit -m "Deploy V5"`
- [ ] `git push origin main`
- [ ] Wait for GitHub Actions

### Post-Deploy
- [ ] Open on mobile browser
- [ ] Test PWA install
- [ ] Check offline mode
- [ ] Verify 60 FPS
- [ ] Test all sections
- [ ] Check analytics

### Mobile Test
- [ ] Chrome (Android)
- [ ] Safari (iOS)
- [ ] Samsung Internet
- [ ] Firefox Mobile
